          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Solar Expansion of Distributed Generation Exponentially Act or the Solar EDGE Act </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to increase for 2 years tax credits that apply to solar property with a nameplate capacity of less than 20 kilowatts. The increases apply to the investment tax credit and the tax credit for residential energy efficient property expenditures. </p>]]></text>
